#  ░░░░░░██  ░██░██ ░░░░░░██  ██░░░░  ██░░░██ ██░░░░
#   ███████  ░██░██  ███████ ░░█████ ░███████░░█████
#  ██░░░░██  ░██░██ ██░░░░██  ░░░░░██░██░░░░  ░░░░░██
# ░░████████ ███░██░░████████ ██████ ░░██████ ██████
#  ░░░░░░░░ ░░░ ░░  ░░░░░░░░ ░░░░░░   ░░░░░░ ░░░░░░

#◦◝◟∘◞◜◦ colors / settings / verbosity
alias \
	cp="cp -irv" \
	diff="diff --color=auto" \
	grep="grep -i --color=auto" \
	ll="ls -AFSho --color=auto --group-directories-first" \
	ls="ls -AFSh --color=auto --group-directories-first" \
	mkdir="mkdir -pv" \
	mv="mv -iv" \
	rm="rm -v" \
	rmfr="rm -frv" \
	yt="yt -fx bestaudio/best" \
	zip="zip -rv"

#◦◝◟∘◞◜◦ shortcuts
alias \
	e='$EDITOR' \
	ka="killall" \
	kx11="sudo pkill -x Xorg" \
	rl="source" \
	sdn="sudo shutdown -h now" \
	se='sudo $EDITOR' \
	smci="sudo make clean install" \
	sx11="startx"

#◦◝◟∘◞◜◦ cfgs
alias \
	cfgalacritty='$EDITOR ~/.config/alacritty/alacritty.yml' \
	cfgaliases='$EDITOR ~/.config/zsh/lib/01-aliases' \
	cfgbinds='$EDITOR ~/.config/sxhkd/sxhkdrc' \
	cfgi3='$EDITOR ~/.config/i3/config' \
	cfgspectrwm='$EDITOR ~/.config/spectrwm/spectrwm.conf' \
	cfgvim='$EDITOR ~/.config/nvim/init.vim' \
	cfgzsh='$EDITOR ~/.config/zsh/.zshrc'

#◦◝◟∘◞◜◦ distro-specific shortcuts
# arch
alias \
	ppaci="sudo pacman -S --needed" \
	ppacr="sudo pacman -R" \
	ppacs="sudo pacman -Ss" \
	ppacu="sudo pacman -Suyy"

# void
alias \
	xxi="sudo xbps-install -S" \
	xxq="xbps-query -s" \
	xxqr="xbps-query -Rs" \
	xxr="sudo xbps-remove" \
	xxu="sudo xbps-install -Su"

#◦◝◟∘◞◜◦ misc
alias \
	ascii="toilet -t -f 3d" \
	future="toilet -t -f future" \
	matrix="cmatrix -b" \
	rusto="toilet -t -f rusto" \
	rustofat="toilet -t -f rustofat" \
	screenkey="screenkey -t 2 -p bottom -s small --opacity 0.55" \
	tnet="ping 1.1.1.1" \
	tnetspeed="speedtest-cli"
